erize the\noutliers of spiked Information-Plus-Noise type models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Jan 2013 22:48:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 6 May 2014 12:42:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-05-07"}
