ton correlation should affect\nthe Cosmic Microwave Background's polarisation at low redshift. An adaption of\nthe here-developed methods to the analysis of irreducible bubble diagrams could\nprove the conjecture of hep-th/0609033 on the termination of the loop expansion\nof thermodynamical quantities at a finite irreducible order.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Jan 2013 09:12:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Feb 2014 12:58:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 18 Apr 2014 09:05:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-06-04"}
